rows.label: tev071601_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: tev071601_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Sen'luarb about Goetia.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071601_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss

rows.label: tev071601_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Sen'luarb about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071601_SEL0031
rows.name: Ask Sen'luarb about life in New LA.

rows.label: tev071601_MSG0001
rows.name: My Ovah trembles at the mere mention of her name.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071601_MSG0002
rows.name:
It seems that Kun'luarb must have been savagely
tortured by her when he served the Ganglion.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071601_MSG0003
rows.name:
And companions of his that were brought with him to
Mira were killed by her for sport.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071601_MSG0004
rows.name: But you have brought her reign of terror to an end?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071601_MSG0005
rows.name:
Then for Kun'luarb, who now resides within me,
allow me to express our deepest gratitude.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071601_MSG0008
rows.name:
Through my Ovah, I have inherited all the intentions
of Kun'luarb.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071601_MSG0009
rows.name:
It now falls upon Sin'luarb and myself to complete his
life's work.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071601_MSG0010
rows.name:
That means overseeing the binary fission of Orphe
in this land until we are uncountable in number.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071601_MSG0011
rows.name:
This will not be an easy task, but with your assistance,
the odds of success are not insignificant. I hope that
you will continue to protect our frail people.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071601_MSG0016
rows.name: I am helping Kon'luarb mass-produce senirapa water.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071601_MSG0017
rows.name:
We owe much to the vast quantities of water purified
by the Biahno water-purification plant.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071601_MSG0018
rows.name:
Without it, producing more senirapa water would
simply not be possible.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071601_MSG0019
rows.name:
I understand that "Ajoa" is the name of the human who
created the plant?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071601_MSG0020
rows.name:
What has become of her? She is a hero to the Orphe,
and I would like to express my gratitude to her.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071601_SEL1021
rows.name: Ask Sen'luarb about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071601_MSG0012
rows.name:
Because of the senirapa water you provided, we have
been able to greatly increase the Orphe population.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071601_MSG0013
rows.name:
But the new red Orpheans are...strange. The memories
given to me from Kun'luarb indicate no familiarity with
such spontaneous mutations.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071601_MSG0014
rows.name:
It is unclear whether such mutations are beneficial to us.
But I must find the answer, so that I might add it to my
Ovah and pass it on to my own divisions.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071601_MSG0015
rows.name:
This is the puzzle that Sin'luarb and I have a duty to
solve. After all, we are the successors of Kun'luarb's
destiny![ST:wait ]
